<body>
    <h1>Pre-Hire (Associate) (Use Case =E2=80=93 UC01)</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h3 id=3D"Pre-Hire(Associate)(UseCase=E2=80=93UC01)-Pre-Hireworkflo=
w">Pre-Hire workflow</h3>
<p>Table-17</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1800" data-layout=3D"center" data-local-id=3D"31=
17baee-e838-428f-938a-761032a3476e" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 361.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 1438.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Type</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Hire&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Description</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Hire use case describes the activities and processes that take place=
 after the candidate accepts the offer but their actual start date for the =
engagement is in the future.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of Attributes&nbsp;</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The following set of attributes represent the tentative set of users=E2=
=80=99 attributes which will be used in the process flow. The final set of =
source and target attributes will be finalized in the design document.</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>First Name</p></li>
<li>
<p>Last Name&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Person Number&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Assignment Status</p></li>
<li>
<p>System Worker Type</p></li>
<li>
<p>Action Name</p></li>
<li>
<p>Hire Date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Effective Date</p></li>
<li>
<p>Department</p></li>
<li>
<p>Position</p></li>
<li>
<p>Location&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Ministry</p></li>
<li>
<p>&nbsp;Workrelationship Primary Flag</p></li>
<li>
<p>Personal Email</p></li>
</ol>
<p>Refer Appendix =E2=80=9C<a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"https://drive=
.google.com/drive/folders/17u4oN4VdyLijziIcn8PMSlUxT5HS_LW0" rel=3D"nofollo=
w"><u>Source and Target Attribute Mapping</u></a>=E2=80=9D for complete lis=
t of attribute mapping.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Pre-Conditions</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>The candidate's offer should be accepted in the Oracle HR system.&nbsp;<=
/p>
<p>The pending worker relationship is generated and assigned a personal num=
ber in the Oracle HR system.&nbsp;</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>When following conditions are true:</p>
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>The Hire Date of the user is within the next 365-days from the current s=
ystem date.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98Assignment status=E2=80=99 attribute should be equal to =E2=80=
=98Active - Payroll Eligible=E2=80=99.</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98System Worker Type=E2=80=99 attribute should be equal to =E2=80=
=98Pending Worker=E2=80=99.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>=E2=80=98Action Name=E2=80=99 attribute should be equal to =E2=80=98Add =
Pending Worker=E2=80=99.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<ol start=3D"1">
<li>
<p>Candidates accept their offer in the Oracle HR system.</p></li>
<li>
<p>The pending worker relationship is generated and assigned a personal num=
ber in the Oracle HR system.</p></li>
<li>
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud data is aggregated into SailPoint IIQ.</p></li>
<li>
<p>A user identity will be created in SailPoint IdentityIQ with =E2=80=98Ac=
tive=E2=80=99 status and WORKRELATIONSHIP_PRIMARY_FLAG will be =E2=80=98Yes=
=E2=80=8B=E2=80=99.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will provision access to ServiceNow and Oracle ERP =
Cloud for My Learning.</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will provision an enabled Active Directory (AD) acc=
ount. Based on the user ministry affiliation, user account will be created =
in a specific domain within AD.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>Azure accounts will be created through AD sync.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will provision SSO identifiers (UPN (User Principal=
 Name) - <a class=3D"external-link" href=3D"mailto:fname.lname@ascension.or=
g" rel=3D"nofollow"><u>fname.lname@ascension.org</u></a>) to the Oracle HR =
system.&nbsp;</p></li>
<li>
<p>SailPoint IdentityIQ will generate a password based on AD password polic=
ies and share the credentials with the user and the NAN leadership mailbox =
team will be notified via email in compliance with Ascension Health Allianc=
e security policy.</p></li>
</ol></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of downstream applications</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Active Directory, Azure, Oracle ERP Cloud, ServiceNow.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Upon receiving a record for a pre-hire, whose Hire Date is within the ne=
xt 365 days from current system date, a SailPoint IdentityIQ account should=
 be created, and access should be provisioned in target applications and us=
er and the NAN leadership mailbox teams are notified with the account detai=
ls.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error handling</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>A ServiceNow ticket will be created and assigned to the Ascension Health=
 Alliance SailPoint IIQ support team.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d9e2f3" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Persona / Actors</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Automated Process</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
<p><strong>Dependency:</strong></p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-table-width=3D"1061" data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"b=
2e998bc-064c-47e2-afa0-c56768b96906" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<colgroup>
<col style=3D"width: 75.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 159.0px;">
<col style=3D"width: 826.0px;">
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>S. no</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Dependency</p></td>
<td data-highlight-colour=3D"#d4deec" class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Point of contact for answers</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>1</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>List of attributes</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to send the final set of attributes ma=
pping.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>2</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Trigger</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required for trigger.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>3</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Basic Flow</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to finalize the attributes and its val=
ues required in the Basic Flow.</p>
<p>Active Directory application team to share the password policies to gene=
rate the password.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>4</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Acceptance criteria</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Oracle HCM Cloud application team to provide users=E2=80=99 demographic =
information and access mapping for pre-hire.</p></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>5</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Error handling</p></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">
<p>Ascension Health Alliance SailPoint IIQ support team to provide ServiceN=
ow Queue.</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<p></p>
